english: China will not attach itself to any big power .
His behavior is nothing out of the ordinary .
chinese: 他的举止没有任何反常。

english: Whatever prospers my business is good .
chinese: 任何使我生意昌隆的都是好的。

english: No great power could run the world .
chinese: 没有任何大国可以操纵这个世界。

english: Any substitute was certain to be worse .
chinese: 任何替代肯定会稍逊一筹的。
任何造句挺难的，這是一个万能造句的方法

english: We are committed to no rigid formula .
chinese: 我们未必矢志坚持任何硬性方案。

english: I meant no reflection on anybody .
chinese: 但我刚才并没有批评任何人的意思。

english: The situation does not permit of any delay .
chinese: 情势不容许任何的拖延。

english: I never discussed another thing with her .
chinese: 我再不同她讨论任何事情了。

english: They refused to be party to any violence .
chinese: 他们拒不参加任何暴力活动。

english: I have done nothing to harm anyone .
chinese: 我没有做过伤害任何人的任何事情。

english: I have been ordered not to let anyone in .
chinese: 我得到吩咐不让任何人入内。

english: They determined to do this at any cost .
chinese: 他们不惜任何牺牲来作此事。

english: Her mind was inevitably at liberty .
chinese: 她的头脑必然是不受任何干扰的。

english: He was not in the humour to seek anything .
chinese: 他没有心情去追求任何东西。
